Build 20011115
=========================

Consequently to bug (), which caused the IDE to go down, I tried to restart my
workspace, and it complained not to be able to restore either the team or the 
debug perspective and ended up with 3 Java perspectives (presumably since I had
made it the default one).

I had unreleased changes, and I got several more stack traces trying to 
interact with the VCM. Apparently the property store got corrupted.
